      "path": "audio/narrations/hilbert-curve/xiaoxiao/construct-con-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35424,
      "text": "再把四条小曲线适当旋转翻转，首尾相接成一条大曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "hilbert-curve",
      "section_id": "locality",
